body:
@thekevinbrown It looks like there's a missing level in your config. The optimizer settings are a subset of `compilers.solc.settings` per example below:
```javascript
 compilers: {
  solc: {
    version: '0.4.24',
    settings: {
      optimizer: {
        enabled: true, // Default: false
        runs: 200      // Default: 200
      },
    }
  }
}
```
